<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٢ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا هِشَامٌ وَشَيْبَانُ، عَنْ يَحْيَى،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَبِي سَلَمَةَ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">سَأَلْتُ عَائِشَةَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَكَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَرْقُدُ وَهُوَ جُنُبٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَتْ:</span> نَعَمْ، وَيَتَوَضَّأُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٤]</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
